Package: amregtest
Title: Runs Allelematch Regression Tests
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Torvald", "Staxler", , "torvald.staxler@telia.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Automates regression testing when testing improvements of
    package \link{allelematch}.\cr\cr Exported functions are prefixed with
    "art" for "allelematch regression test".\cr \cr The exported functions
    are: \link{artVersion}, \link{artList} and \link{artRun}.  \cr\cr The
    tests are based on \link{testthat}. The tests use data sets as input.
    These data sets are stored within the package. See \link{artData}
    \cr\cr The results of the tests are compared with pre-stored results,
    recorded with variants of \link{expect_snapshot}.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports: 
    allelematch,
    remotes,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    utils,
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
